<br>
She, unlike her brother was more invollved in the basic issues and developments in the war, not the number of casulties it provided.<br>
<br>
She glanced lightly at Eris and Artemis and decided to speak with her elder sister.<br>
<br>
&quot;Artemis, may I have a word?&quot;<br>
